{"tid":1446730,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［拋磚引玉］下一步仲可以點升級？睇下美國反越戰運動點做","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:55:30.000Z","uid":82387,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"382ddd105c612157f823716f48c6b91bb6697821","tid":1446730,"uid":82387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1969 年，正值美國反越戰運動高峰期，活躍社運的反戰僱主 Jerome Grossman 提出，要發動全國大罷市反對越戰，策略是每個月罷市一日，若然政府一個月內未有讓步，下個月則罷市兩日，如此類推，罷市日數不斷遞增。</span><br />\n<br />\n我地8.5罷得一次 就會有第二、第三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府再唔回應訴求 我地就以長期戰還擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次罷工成功unlock左機場呢個俾到政府最大壓力嘅核心戰略地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我建議下次罷工繼續由最打得嘅航空業領軍 癱瘓機場運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />配合九月開學罷課造勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下政府可以忍幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s. 下次罷工仲塞唔塞鐵值得深思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終今次係民意戰 我覺得淨係主攻機場都夠打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cf7fe41b33e809fe6d7f7d0651446040a0a62e","tid":1446730,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92dae07468b27ea71c88c386b008679b2f2d7bdb","tid":1446730,"uid":82387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:17:51.000Z","msg":"戰術post 歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90443ec525d86a4591dddaba9158917c8eeb2d2","tid":1446730,"uid":145675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:19:52.000Z",